channel.title: Closed for now
channel.description:
Not making graphics for a while
I'm a bit bored, I have all Saturday, and I want to work on some graphics.. There for, I'm having my own little graphics thread. I'm pretty experienced with PhotoShop so don't hold back :P
You can give me a basic idea or fill out this little form thingy [code] [b]Picture Size (Width by Height):[/b]
[b]Theme:[/b]
[b]Picture/Render (I can render it for you):[/b]
[b]Color one:[/b]
[b]Color two:[/b]
[b]Color three?:[/b]
[b]Gradients:[/b]
[b]Style (Pop, soft, cool colors/warm colors etc..):[/b]
[b]Text one:[/b]
[b]Text one size:[/b]
[b]Text one color:[/b]
[b]Text one spot on picture:[/b]
[b]Text two:[/b]
[b]Text two size:[/b]
[b]Text two color:[/b]
[b]Text two spot on picture:[/b] [/code] If you want more text on it just tell me ;)
All of the spots on the form thing are optional, you can give me a little of what you want on it and let me do the rest. I really would prefer you give me the whole thing you want, because sometimes it's hard for me to come up with stuff for a picture :o
